{"tid":248842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"妙齡女打網咖睡著　嚇醒後竟發現「內褲消失」","createTime":"2017-05-19T01:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T03:51:54.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d893ead8a33dbcd02361982ef4e920c5e1145027","tid":248842,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"日本兵庫縣神戶市一名女子日前在網咖睡著，醒來以後發現內褲被人偷走，嚇得馬上請網咖店員調閱監視器，發現是同網咖的一名30歲男客所做。警方隨後逮捕男子，但他卻用自己喝醉，不知道發生甚麼事情的藉口來否認犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據《神戶新聞》報導，事情發生在17日凌晨，25歲的女子在網咖包廂內睡著，另一個包廂內的男客人趁機闖入，將女子的內褲偷走藏起。女子醒來以後發現內褲不見，找網咖店員調監視器，比對後確認是一名男客所為，馬上報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場以後先搜查男客的包廂，在他的椅墊下找到內褲，但男客卻否認犯罪，說自己喝醉了，不知道發生了甚麼事情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://giant.gfycat.com/SilkyAcceptableFiddlercrab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgiant.gfycat.com%2FSilkyAcceptableFiddlercrab.gif&h=35517cbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5f5af2d4d78bbddc9ee8f7775f33f46fbc0f169","tid":248842,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:12:50.000Z","msg":"訓到比人除左底褲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cec21fdc68a93a1b900318546cea47faf244bbd","tid":248842,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓到比人除左底褲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n訓到比除左人底褲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557b8df8250b488b1f8d1fb9ad97413293404cc7","tid":248842,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓到比人除左底褲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n訓到除左人條底褲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55a27c1a4d368d92f85715e39774ce3fa9908ce","tid":248842,"uid":44301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"話說呢，有冇人睇到25歲都稱得上妙齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}